<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_421_r1l7"><expan>Wolgeborn<ex>er</ex></expan> lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr gnade ſchrıftlıch <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l8">begert hat an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> ʒuerfarn auf welche ʒeıt ſıe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l9">eins tags gen <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell warten <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> vor <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> . <expan>Marggr<ex>af</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l11"><expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> etc / Das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> ʒu dıenſt alſo an </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l12">ſıe bracht dıe <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vns <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> . ſıe <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnedıg<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l13">~ den <expan>Marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> . ſo mug Jn eẅr edel auch <expan>bıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> . eẅch <expan>beıd<ex>er</ex>ſeıt</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l14"><expan>hıeʒwıſch<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>Pfıngſt<ex>en</ex></expan> ſchıerıſt . ʒu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> . tag für ſein gnade <expan>ʒuſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l15">ʒu <expan>ſölıche<ex>m</ex></expan> tag <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe denn ʒu <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> . Als denn eẅr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l16">gnade begert hat ʒu <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> Ob ewr edel vnd dıe <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> die ʒeıt ſıcher vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l17">Jn ſeyn etc darcʒu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> vns dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l18">eẅr edel <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ʒeıt vor Jn ſıcher ſeın ſülle / Alſo daʒ ſıe vnd dıe Jren vor </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l19"><expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> auch ſıcher ſein / Welch der <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> denn bey Jren vnd der ıren <expan>ſchede<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l20">niht <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> ſein . dıe <expan>ſülle<ex>n</ex></expan> ʒu voran . ſıcher vor Jn ſein als pıllıch ıſt . <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l21">aber etlıch der <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey Jren vnd der ıren <expan>ſchede<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>geweſ<ex>en</ex></expan> / wenn Jn dıe be = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l22">nennet <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan> ſo <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſıe darcʒu auch <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> / VVas <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l23">darinn ſein wıl das mugt Jr vns bey dıſem <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreıben</expan> . Denn wo </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l24">wır <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>gedıene<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möcht<ex>en</ex></expan> des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wır wıllıg . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l25"><expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nıca</expan> Judıca </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l26">Sebold <expan>Jm<ex>m</ex></expan> hof vnd Conrad </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_421_r1l27">hersſpruker ʒu <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_421" id="209v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von Plawen, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
                        zu Küngswart, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> lieben
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Wolgeborn<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>,
                        als uns ewr gnade schriftlich <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan> und begert
                        hat, an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> zu
                        erfarn, auf welche zeit sie eins tags gen <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        edell warten <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> vor
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>marggr<ex>af</ex></expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Brandemb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>,
                        etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu dienst also an sie bracht. Die
                                <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> uns
                        <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, sie <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> den
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> den <expan>marggraf<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan>, so mug in ewr edel auch
                                <expan>bitte<ex>n</ex></expan>, ewch
                            <expan>beid<ex>er</ex>seit</expan>
<expan>hiezwisch<ex>en</ex></expan>
<app><note><q type="date"><expan>pfingst<ex>en</ex></expan> schierist</q>31.05.1422</note></app> zu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>hören</expan> tag für sein gnade <expan>zu
                                secze<ex>n</ex></expan>, zu <expan>söliche<ex>m</ex></expan> tag
                                <expan>meyne<ex>n</ex></expan> sie denn zu
                            <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>; als denn ewr gnade begert hat zu
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, ob ewr edel und die
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> die zeit sicher vor in seyn etc.,
                        darczu <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> uns die
                            <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>
<expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>tt</expan>, daz ewr edel
                            <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> zeit vor in sicher sein sülle, also daz
                        sie und die iren vor <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> auch sicher sein, welch der
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> denn bey iren und der iren
                                <expan>schede<ex>n</ex></expan> niht <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        sein, die <expan>sülle<ex>n</ex></expan> zu voran sicher vor in sein, als
                        pillich ist; <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> aber etlich der
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> bey iren und der iren
                                <expan>schede<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan>, wenn in die benennet
                            <expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan>, so <expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan> sie
                        darczu auch <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan>. Was
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell <expan>meynu<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        darinn sein wil, das mugt ir uns bey disem <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreiben</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gediene<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möcht<ex>en</ex></expan>, des <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wir
                        willig. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> judica. <lb/>Sebold
                            <expan>Im<ex>m</ex>hof</expan> und Conrad Hersspruker zu
                                <expan>Nuremb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
